However, you can make the job a bit easier if you do a little bit of planning and research. First narrow down exactly what you want the filter to do. Do you merely want to filter your drinking water or do you want to remove contaminants from all the water you use including your shower water, cooking water, and water for washing clothes? Take the time to find out what contaminants may be in your water and how they can effect your health – not only when you are drinking it but when you are breathing the fumes and showering in it as well. Description: Black Lotus Ventures is a creative agency that manifests its mantra: Own your power, give back, leave no stone unturned.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Atlanta Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Black Lotus Ventures is a testament to creativity, powering up the world with its mantra: Harness your strength, contribute positively, and leave no trail unexplored. Our forte lies in the realm of design, functioning as a conduit between customers and the brands they love, using our U/X design expertise. Your ideas set the stage; we amplify them, molding experiences that resonate with your target audience. With us, launching your product is a seamless journey marked by precision and flair. Our creative talent transcends boundaries, illuminating the world of websites, application development, and brand marketing. In web creation, we turn your vision into an immersive digital experience. Our development expertise converts the raw sketches of your ideas into the finished framework of a hassle-free project. The third facet of our expertise lies in brand marketing, where we breathe life into your promotional videos, social campaigns, and product launch assets. We at Black Lotus are a band of entrepreneurs united by the shared passion for untangling complex problems. We blend an eclectic mix of skills to shape groundbreaking ideas into tangible realities. Our creative process is designed around five exact steps. We begin with design and development, diligently listening to and aligning your vision with the project goals. Market research follows next, where we decode the needs of your target audience and analyze the competitive landscape. This research guides us through the following stages of conceptualization and creativity, where we dig deep into the data to comprehend how users interact with your product. Design forms the fourth step, transforming your vision into palpable layouts and assets. The final development stage ensues, marked by stringent quality controls that ensure a flawless launch of your product. Since 2012, the creative wizards of Black Lotus have championed the cause of visionaries determined to make a difference. For instance, amidst the pandemic-stricken world of 2020, we designed a unique social media platform, Seventh Ave, encapsulating the global black experience. With the NCAA regulations lifted in 2021, we facilitated the creation of MOGL, supporting its journey toward venture capital funding and securing collaborations with big names like Adidas and Nike. Our prowess extends beyond these triumphs, as we’ve helped HR innovator Knac with their website, making the hiring process bias-free. From conducting market research for Messenger to handling social media for an audience exceeding 100K, Black Lotus’ creative solutions have touched millions across the globe. We're proud to be a part of such impactful transformations, consistently affirming our mission to empower visionaries worldwide.

Headquarters Regions: Greater Seattle Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Playmark is the world's first athlete marketplace. There is a disconnect today between social media platforms that enable athletes to make a name for themselves and the opportunity to monetize personal brand value. Playmark's marketplace bridges the gap by making business deals involving athletes as easy as e-commerce. Professional athletes can now sell official rights, content, and access. What began as a strategic partnership with the NFL Players Association became a new venture when George Aposporos and Erik Bergsagel founded Playmark in December 2010. Playmark's online and mobile platform was built from ground up to increase access to the largest professional roster in America: over 2,000 NFL players. Playmark has a multi-year exclusive with NFL Players. Since the launch of Playmark.com in October of 2011, Playmark has reduced the average time to close a licensing deal with NFL Players from 35 weeks down to 2. The record time to close a deal is 3 days--as fast as buying a pair of shoes online.  Located near the world famous Pike Place Market in Seattle, Playmark is privately funded from strategic partners and angel investors.

Description: Westbourne Investment Advisors is an investment advisory firm.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Baltimore-Maryland Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Westbourne Investment Advisors provides a personalized approach to developing and managing client investment portfolios. Prior to managing a portfolio they review a client's investment goals and return objectives to determine a suitable asset allocation. Key factors in portfolio construction include a client's age, income requirements, income tax picture, estate planning objectives, and risk tolerance. Their commitment is to the ongoing supervision of a limited number of client portfolios. Managing no pooled assets gives their advisors greater flexibility in account supervision. The close relationship with their clients aids them in selecting the most suitable investments to achieve each client's desired investment results.
